des:
If you have any problem when you use this skill, you can contact us with email : simon_smart@simon.com.cn

The Simon Smart products work together to help you control home appliances nice and easy.

You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light, control the switch and socket, open the curtain, air-condition the temperature, check the humidity, control the IR remote controller, monitor through the camera, check the door state, and trigger the presetted scene.

There's no need to walk to the appliance - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show.After connecting Alexa to your Simon Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1) Download our Simon Smart app in Google Play or Apple Store;
(2) Register one Simon Smart account in our Simon Smart app;
(3) You need to have some Simon Smart devices in hand;
(4) Configure these devices in our Simon Smart app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in Simon Smart skills;
(5) Download Amazon Alexa app from Google Play, Apple Store or Amazon app market;
(6) Configure Echo with Alexa app;
(7) Search Simon Smart skill from the Alexa app skills category;
(8) Click Enable skill of Simon Smart, and you'll be navigated to Simon login page;
(9) Input your Simon Smart account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10) Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on kitchen light"
“Alexa, turn off kitchen light"
“Alexa, dim livingroom light"
“Alexa, brighten livingroom light"
“Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
“Alexa, set bedroom light to Blue"
“Alexa, turn on bedroom air conditioner"

Currently this skill supports products:
smart switch,
smart socket, 
smart bulb....
